Rapper Cassper Nyovest whose real name is Refiloe Phoolo, shared a warm message to Keith Bothongo on his Twitter account. The 29-year-old Maftown born Hip Hop artist shared with his followers that Keith has been a great influence on him. The musician said he looks up to him and takes him as his second father. Cassper also added that the businessman has shown him love and he is a man of principles. Keith Bothongo is the founder of Bothongo Group BG which is a commercial and residential property development company. The Doc Shebeleza hitmaker is also preparing himself for his annual #FillUp event that will take place in his home province. Cassper Nyovest shared that this year’s Fill Up will be taking place at the Royal Bafokeng stadium in Rustenburg. 